products/cmi/send-policy.html.title: 1.1 SendPolicy Method
products/cmi/send-policy.html.body:
SendPolicy Method

Business Logic





Note


The user must ensure that the username is present in the system, the corresponding password is correct and the account is eligible for sale.

Required items can not be missing, for special fields have format requirements as well as the length of requirements.
 Otherwise eBaoCloud will return the following errors.

Require filed is missing. 
ErrorCode=“4” 
ErrorMessage like "Require field. Field name xxx is null or empty."

Validation Error.
ErrorCode=“5” 
ErrorMessage like "Validation Error. Field name xxx is xxx."

Master Data can not be found.
ErrorCode=“7” 
ErrorMessage like "DATA not found in Master Table. xxx"

Other Business Error from eBaoCloud back-end
ErrorCode=“9999”



If you want to generate policyNo by yourself, you must inform eBaoCloud in advance and you will always generate policyNo for future use.
